Cancer of the colon and rectum in the first three decades of life.

Shahrudin MD(1), Noori SM.

Author information:
(1)Department of Surgery; Royal Postgraduate Medical School, United Kingdom.

BACKGROUND/AIMS: Recently an increasing number of young colorectal carcinoma 
